A cyberpunk-style digital workspace scene showing a glowing holographic lotus flower emerging from the center of a dark, neon-lit computer interface. The interface displays cascading layers of translucent panels with color swatches and UI elements floating in mid-air, bathed in electric blue and hot pink neon glows. Circuit board patterns weave through the background like roots beneath the lotus. A hacker's hands hover over a floating keyboard, manipulating the petals of the lotus which transform into customizable interface elements. Rain streaks across a window in the background, reflecting the vibrant colors. The mood is rebellious creativity meets digital craftsmanship.
